Class ReadOnlyBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.ReadOnlyBlackboardView

  • public class ReadOnlyBlackboardView
extends java.lang.Object
    View of the Blackboard only allowing reading access. Writing access isn't provided.
    See Also:
    for information about Blackboard views
